metadata.name: Creature Of The Night
metadata.description:
Searching in the darkness 
Running from the day 
Hiding from tomorrow
Nothing left to say 

Victim of the moment
Future deep in doubt 
Living in a whisper
Til , start to shout 
I AM CREATURE OF THE NIGHT 

technique : Imaginary illustration , Digital painting
